CODE.item: CONCATENATE WA_DADOS-VDATUM+6(2) ' / ' WA_DADOS-VDATUM+4(2) ' / ' WA_DADOS-VDATUM+2(2) INTO GV_DATE SEPARATED BY SPACE.
CONCATENATE WA_DADOS-VEZEITERF(2) ':' WA_DADOS-VEZEITERF+2(2) INTO GV_TIME SEPARATED BY SPACE.
CONCATENATE sy-datum+6(2) ' / ' sy-datum+4(2) ' / ' sy-datum+2(2) INTO GV_DATE2 SEPARATED BY SPACE.
CONCATENATE sy-uzeit(2) ':' sy-uzeit+2(2) INTO GV_TIME2 SEPARATED BY SPACE.
